# 诗云 / Poetry Cloud — build-time environment (all optional; copy to .env.local to use)
#
# The app is static by default. The ONLY optional server touchpoint is feedback collection.
# Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the client bundle at build time, so this URL is PUBLIC — point it at a
# write-only collector (Cloudflare Worker / Formspree), never at anything that needs a secret.
#
# Leave unset (or blank) to keep the build 100% static: feedback then lives only in the visitor's
# localStorage (owner reads it on-device via the hidden 5-taps-on-logo gesture).
#
# When set, each submitted feedback message is ALSO POSTed as JSON: {source:"shiyun", message, ts}
# See docs/DEPLOY.md §feedback for a ready-to-paste Cloudflare Worker.
# VITE_FEEDBACK_ENDPOINT="https://shiyun-feedback.<your-subdomain>.workers.dev"
